Description: This is a Alder wood body Telecaster style guitar with a Mighty Might Fender licensed neck. The tuners are Gotoh, and the pickups are Lindy Fralin standard Telecaster. The Bridge is all Fender including the saddles. The guitar is wired with a 3 way selector switch one volume one tone. The condition is solid and the giutar plays and sounds good. The Nitro cellulose lacquer finish could use some sanding and polishing There are many coats of finish and white nitro lacquer Primer on this guitar (Midnight Wine from ReRanch). Their are some sanding spots and a bad scratch on the back of the guitar, Please see the photos for more finish condition issues. PayPal only. Will ship to the U.S. only. These pickups offer 50’s tone. Expect clear and clean tone with a chime and bell-like quality. Our manufacturing process allows us to achieve unparalleled quality control.
